OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA largely dry day with variable
OL,6,Fcloud and sunny spells. The odd
OL,7,Fisolated shower possible, the main
OL,8,Frisk being during this afternoon.
OL,9,FFeeling warm again.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FMostly dry and bright this
OL,12,Fevening, though a few spots of rain
OL,13,Fnot to be ruled out, mainly across
OL,14,FTayside. A risk of further showers
OL,15,Ftowards dawn.
OL,16,
OL,17,CMonday:FMainly cloudy in the morning
OL,18,Fwith a few showery outbreaks of rain.
OL,19,FTurning brighter but with a risk of
OL,20,Ffurther showers in the afternoon, some
OL,21,Fpossibly heavy and thundery.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
